Uses of Package
high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.design

  • Packages that use high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.design 
    Package Description
    high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.compilers
    This packages contains most of the actual compiler implementation.
    high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.exceptions
    This package contains special exceptions that may be thrown during compilation.
    high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem
    This package is a concrete implementation of Autumn's type-system.
    high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.typesystem.design
    This package contains the design of the Autumn programming language's type-system.
    high.mackenzie.autumn.lang.compiler.utils
    This package contains utility code that is needed by the compiler implementation.
